import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import Card from './Cards';

ReactDOM.render(
    <>
        <Card imgsrc='https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51Y-4b1Ux0L._SY450_.jpg'
            title='A Netflix Original Series'
            sname='DARK'
            link='https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80100172'
        />
        <Card imgsrc='https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDcxOGI0MDYtNTc5NS00NDUzLWFkOTItNDIxZjI0OTllNTljXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTMxODk2OTU@._V1_.jpg'
            title='A Netflix Original Series'
            sname='Money Heist'
            link='https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80192098'
        />
        <Card imgsrc='https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/71OB1IywjLL._AC_SY679_.jpg'
            title='A Netflix Original Series'
            sname='Stranger Things'
            link='https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80057281'
        />
        <Card imgsrc='https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/VJmYaPHxqr7j_qmbLJk139ZeZ2RCGYy4dRVKzMvdzKreRiUNtXvsP0TIPdNuwUi7eoy1z_9X_Xmz_kgmaFSltqQF2oUPOQc'
            title='A Netflix Original Series'
            sname='YOU'
            link='https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80211991'
        />

    </>
    ,
    document.getElementById('root')
)
